HEADWORD: Olefiant
<hw>O*le"fi*ant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>ol⟦eacute⟧fiant</ets>, fr.L. <ets>oleum</ets> oil +
